com.hpe.caf.worker.document.model

Interface Subdocuments

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DocumentWorkerObject, Iterable<Subdocument>

    public interface Subdocuments
extends DocumentWorkerObject, Iterable<Subdocument>
    Represents the list of subdocuments that are attached to a document.

      • get

        @Nonnull
Subdocument get(int index)
        Retrieves the subdocument at the specified position.

        Note that if a subdocument in the list is deleted that this will affect the positions of the subdocuments which follow it in the subdocument list.

        Parameters:
        index - index of the subdocument to return
        Returns:
        the subdocument at the specified position
        Throws:
        IndexOutOfBoundsException - if the index is out of range (index < 0 || index >= size())
